{"info":{"title":"[php]glob函数","date":1564045020,"tags":"php"},"path":"./source/_posts/php-glob.md","content":"<h2 id=\"定义和用法\">定义和用法</h2>\n<p>glob() 函数返回匹配指定模式的文件名或目录。</p>\n<p>该函数返回一个包含有匹配文件 / 目录的数组。如果出错返回 false。</p>\n<!--more-->\n\n<h3 id=\"语法\">语法</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"hljs-function\"><span class=\"hljs-title\">glob</span><span class=\"hljs-params\">(pattern,flags)</span></span>\n</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"例子-1\">例子 1</h2>\n<pre><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&lt;?php</span>\nprint_r(glob(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;*.txt&quot;</span>));\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">?&gt;</span></code></pre>\n<p>输出类似:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"hljs-built_in\">Array</span>\n(\n[<span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>] =&gt; target.txt\n[<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>] =&gt; source.txt\n[<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>] =&gt; test.txt\n[<span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>] =&gt; test2.txt\n)</code></pre>\n","nav":[[2,"定义和用法"],[3,"语法"],[2,"例子 1"]]}